iv><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif">Once you have submitted a response you will be unable to amend it so please read carefully before submitting.&nbsp;</font></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: tahoma, sans-serif;">You can only submit one response per contract.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px;">Once an acceptance is submitted, an enforceable contract has been entered into between yourself and The Challenge.</span></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif"><font color="#222222" face="arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12.727272033691406px;">1. We are pleased to be able to offer you a contract of volunteering on NCS with The Challenge summer programme. &nbsp;Each contract is for a fixed term and the beginning and end date for each fixed term are set out in the timetable ( <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/MyRole.aspx">your Timetable is available on the Staffing&nbsp;</a></span></font><font color="#222222"><span style="font-size: 12.800000190734863px;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/MyRole.aspx">Website</a></span></font><font color="#222222" face="arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12.727272033691406px;">). Each September day is regarded as a separate contract, therefore you may receive up to 8 contracts. Please submit a response for all contracts.&nbsp;</span></font></font></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px;"><br></span></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px;">2. Each employment contract is made up from the applicable parts of this section, and&nbsp;</span>2014 Project Volunteer Agreement<span style="font-family: tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;that is attached to this email.</span></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></div><div class="gmail_default" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.727272033691406px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="tahoma, sans-serif">3. Your volunteering cannot commence until we have received (1) two satisfactory references; (2) an enhanced DBS check; (3) a copy of the enclosed terms confirming your acceptance of each contract; Please see the Terms and Conditions for details of what constitutes satisfactory evidence. If you fail to do so you will be unable to commence volunteering. If this is problematic please contact your local staffing team.&